sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/CLI/MCP)
    participant API as Eval Hub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Init as eval-runtime-init
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Adapter as Eval Adapter<br/>(lm-eval/lighteval)
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar<br/>localhost:8080 HTTP
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,OCI: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Submission

    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s TokenReview)
    API->>API: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview
    API->>DB: Store evaluation record<br/>Auth: Password
    API->>MLflow: Create experiment<br/>Auth: Bearer token
    MLflow-->>API: Experiment ID
    API->>K8s: Create Job + ConfigMap<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>API: Job created

    Note over Init,S3: Init Container (if test_data_ref)
    K8s->>Init: Start init container
    Init->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>Init: Test data files
    Init-->>K8s: Init complete

    Note over Adapter,OCI: Evaluation Execution
    K8s->>Adapter: Start adapter + sidecar
    K8s->>Sidecar: Start sidecar (native, KEP-753)

    Adapter->>Sidecar: Run benchmarks<br/>HTTP localhost:8080 (plaintext, no auth)

    Note over Client,OCI: Flow 2: Evaluation Status Callback

    Adapter->>Sidecar: POST status update<br/>HTTP localhost:8080 (plaintext)
    Sidecar->>API: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token, HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    API->>DB: Update job status<br/>Auth: Password

    Note over Sidecar,OCI: Result Tracking & Artifact Export

    Sidecar->>MLflow: Log metrics/params<br/>Auth: Projected SA token, HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Sidecar->>OCI: Push artifacts<br/>Auth: Docker config.json, HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Adapter-->>Sidecar: Evaluation complete
    Sidecar->>API: Final status update<br/>Auth: SA token, HTTPS
    API->>DB: Mark job completed
    API-->>Client: Job status: completed
